    this Act;

    (5) the repeal of the 1033 Program under Section 306 of Title III of this
    Act; and

    (6) the Constitutional Safe Harbor under Section 502 of this Title,
    retroactive to the date of introduction of this Act in Congress.

(c) SCHEDULED EFFECTIVE DATES.-- The following provisions shall take effect on
